%% 时序图：N 个角色之间的对话/调用顺序
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User / 用户
    participant API as Gateway
    participant SVC as Service
    participant DB as Database

    U->>API: 1. POST /resource (request)
    activate API
    API->>SVC: 2. validate + dispatch
    activate SVC
    SVC->>DB: 3. SELECT ...
    DB-->>SVC: rows
    SVC-->>API: 4. response payload
    deactivate SVC
    API-->>U: 5. 200 OK
    deactivate API

    Note over U,DB: 同步调用链；失败时返回 4xx/5xx
